<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home - HuaHeihei</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Rokkitt:wght@400&family=Source+Sans+Pro:wght@500&family=Khula:wght@300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav>
            <div class="container">
                <a href="/" class="logo">HuaHeihei</a>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="#about">About Us</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#products">Our Products</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </nav>
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h1 style="color: #FFFFFF;">Welcome to HuaHeihei</h1>
                <p>Discover the finest quality, nutritious, and ethically sourced chicken eggs.</p>
                <a href="/signup" class="btn-primary">Shop Now</a>`
            </div>
        </section>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section id="about" class="section-about">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>About Us</h2>
                <div class="about-content">
                    <img src="/images/farm.jpg" alt="Farm">
                    <p>At HuaHeihei, we are dedicated to providing the highest quality chicken eggs that are both nutritious and ethically sourced. Our commitment to quality and sustainability sets us apart as a trusted brand in the industry.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section id="products" class="section-products">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Our Products</h2>
                <div class="product-cards">
                    <div class="card">
                        <img src="/images/premium-eggs.jpg" alt="Premium Eggs">
                        <h3>Premium Eggs</h3>
                        <p>Our premium eggs are rich in nutrients and perfect for any recipe.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <img src="/images/organic-eggs.jpg" alt="Organic Eggs">
                        <h3>Organic Eggs</h3>
                        <p>Fresh and organic eggs that meet our high ethical standards.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <img src="/images/specialty-eggs.jpg" alt="Specialty Eggs">
                        <h3>Specialty Eggs</h3>
                        <p>Unique and specialty eggs for gourmet cooking and baking.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section id="contact" class="section-contact">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Contact Us</h2>
                <p>If you have any questions or would like to get in touch with us, please don't hesitate to contact us through the form below or via email.</p>
                <form action="/contact" method="POST">
                    <label for="name">Name</label>
                    <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
                   
                    <label for="email">Email</label>
                    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
                   
                    <label for="message">Message</label>
                    <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" required></textarea>
                   
                    <button type="submit" class="btn-primary">Send Message</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2024 HuaHeihei. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
